info.description:
JiraRobot is a robot library for interacting with
JIRA through the use of jirapython and JIRA REST API
        
Test script is available inside the distribution under the 'JiraRobot/Tests' directory or 'C:/Python27/JiraRobotTests' after installing.


View the full README at: http://navinet.github.io/JiraRobot

Keyword Documentation: http://navinet.github.io/JiraRobot/JiraRobot-KeywordDocumentation.html
info.keywords: robotframework robot testing testautomation jira restapi jirarobot
